author: imario
msg: changed the way how the webdav resources are fetched, and a better handling of how the childlist is processed.
This allows e.g. to determine the type and lastmoddate of restricted resources.
Browsing through a webdav tree should be significant faster than before as many, many round-trips have been saved.

msg: getScheme - mime-type: changed to new contentInfo
